<span id="freeTextContainer11793303803855600988">*<br/><a href='http://www.hawes.com/2005/2005-10-23.pdf' rel='nofollow noopener'>NYT Best Seller List - 10/23/2005 - #1</a><br/><a href='https://www.goodreads.com/list/show/8720.Best_by_Michael_Connelly' rel='nofollow noopener'>Goodreads - Best by Michael Connelly list - #1</a><br/><a href='https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1189340/' rel='nofollow noopener'>IMDB - Book used in The Lincoln Lawyer movie</a><br/><a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H27t-pYOavw' rel='nofollow noopener'>YouTube 🍿The Lincoln Lawyer movie trailer</a><br/><br/><a href='https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=2&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjjqYGiyYPnAhVOwlkKHVXwDpYQwqsBMAF6BAgKEAc&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL6P1WtMVa8s&amp;usg=AOvVaw0_syTjXondSrbQp0LY6MWA%20' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Lincoln Lawyer (2011) – Opening Title Sequence - great</a><br/><br/>The book is great but I liked the movie much more than most others do...<br/><br/>Micky Haller - The Lincoln Lawyer - in his expensive Lincoln Town car, charges high retainers &amp; bails for clients to “Get out of jail” just like Monopoly. But you don’t get money back innocent or guil</span>
  <span id="freeText11793303803855600988" style="display:none">*<br><a href="http://www.hawes.com/2005/2005-10-23.pdf" rel="nofollow noopener">NYT Best Seller List - 10/23/2005 - #1</a><br><a href="https://www.goodreads.com/list/show/8720.Best_by_Michael_Connelly" rel="nofollow noopener">Goodreads - Best by Michael Connelly list - #1</a><br><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1189340/" rel="nofollow noopener">IMDB - Book used in The Lincoln Lawyer movie</a><br><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H27t-pYOavw" rel="nofollow noopener">YouTube 🍿The Lincoln Lawyer movie trailer</a><br><br><a href="https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=web&amp;cd=2&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjjqYGiyYPnAhVOwlkKHVXwDpYQwqsBMAF6BAgKEAc&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL6P1WtMVa8s&amp;usg=AOvVaw0_syTjXondSrbQp0LY6MWA%20" rel="nofollow noopener">The Lincoln Lawyer (2011) – Opening Title Sequence - great</a><br><br>The book is great but I liked the movie much more than most others do...<br><br>Micky Haller - The Lincoln Lawyer - in his expensive Lincoln Town car, charges high retainers &amp; bails for clients to “Get out of jail” just like Monopoly. But you don’t get money back innocent or guilty, they are non-refundable, going to the Lawyer fee &amp; court.<br> <blockquote>
